snippet.title: Three More Boards Revealed in Mario Party Superstars! – Nintendo Switch – Nintendo Direct 9.23.21
snippet.description:
0:00 - Intro
🌲  0:16 - Woody Woods
🏝 0:24 - Yoshi’s Tropical Island 
😈  0:33 - Horror Land
⛰️  0:43 - Mt. Minigames 

Three more boards from the Nintendo 64 era join Space Land and Peach’s Birthday Cake in Mario Party Superstars! Also, want to focus on minigame action? Head to Mt. Minigames for a variety of courses!

Available 10/29 on Nintendo Switch. https://marioparty.nintendo.com/
